my final skill tree will be like this most likely<br>
<br>
39 c/s: for last chain off perf. <br>
35 stealth: with rvr bonus going in to skill,plus +skill items,easy to raise. <br>
34 sword: 34 style is decent to support other styles,and with +10 from rvr/skill items will be near max damage.<br>
